	<ScenarioDef>
		<defName>OC_PMCEx-member</defName>
		<label>PMC ex-member</label>
		<description>You have been killing people for money for a long time, but your contract is over and you want to rest. After taking your last paycheck, you decide to buy a spaceship and start traveling. Maybe in search of a better life, or maybe just interesting finds. With your faithful dog, you leave the Catharsis base and head for the nearest orbital station. The money was enough only for the cheapest ship, on which you rushed into the abysses of endless space. However, your wanderings did not last long, at one moment, because of a sharp blurring of consciousness, you could not avoid an asteroid flying at you. The stone got right into the engine and now you have to save your life. You and your four-legged friend jump into an escape pod and head for the nearest planet.</description>
		<scenario>
			<summary>A PMC fighter, a loyal dog, a small supply of resources, can you survive?</summary>
			<playerFaction>
				<def>PlayerFaction</def>
				<factionDef>PlayerColony</factionDef>
