		<description>You were guilty before your first homeland, therefore, your dear and humane government decided to send you to an "operation", the purpose of which, as they said, was to remove your memory and make you a brainless dummy. And although you do not remember the people who performed the operation on you, do not remember the place of the operation, you can say with confidence that it failed, otherwise emergency lighting would not be working in the corridors of the station now. Going out into these very corridors, you heard random shooting, heavy footsteps and a lot of screams. Unfortunately, you were still not yourself due to anesthesia, so you walked slowly in a blissful state, looking at corpses, blood and lamps barely illuminating your path. After a while, you were found. Those who raided this station picked you up and took you away with them. They were from the once great Empire. They thought that the operation was successfully completed on you, and began to train you diligently, as if you were some kind of child. However, they told you a lot of things that you couldn't even think about when you were on your home planet.</description>
